      <title>中国家电巨头美的集团在香港上市，募资 40 亿美元，股价上涨 9.5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/chinese-appliance-giant-midea-set-to-trade-in-hong-kong-after-raising-4-billion</link>
